msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:167
msgid ""
"![Photograph of action, with banner \"Cows Against "
"Coal.\"](/assets/uploads/9.jpg)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:169
msgid ""
"The giant global dairy corporation Fonterra was greeted with [drums, cow "
"costumes, placards and a pile of "
"coal](https://www.facebook.com/XR.Chch/videos/1468110950055597/), as XR "
"Ōtautahi (Christchurch) asked the question: Why are Fonterra still using "
"coal in a climate emergency?"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:171
#, no-wrap
msgid "**3 JUL | Ibiza, Spain**\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:173
msgid ""
"![Photograph of action, rebels with their heads in the "
"sand.](/assets/uploads/5.jpg)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:175
msgid ""
"XR Ibiza put their heads in the sand at Playa d’en Bossa “to alert citizens "
"and request urgent media and institutional action in the face of the Climate "
"Emergency.”"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:177
msgid ""
"[Read full Unchained "
"here.](https://rebellion.global/blog/2020/07/16/xr-unchained-16/)"
