#. type: Title ##
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:182
#, no-wrap
msgid "UK. The Rebellion Returns"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:185
#, no-wrap
msgid "**28 AUG & 01 SEP | London, Wales (TBC)**\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:187
msgid "![XR pink graphic, \"We Want To Live.\"](/assets/uploads/8.png)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:189
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**From September 1st we will peacefully blockade the UK Parliamen**t in "
"London and Cardiff until they promise that the first thing they'll do is "
"pass our 3 demands into law. We’ll keep the blockade going for as long as it "
"takes, so take two weeks off starting from the 1st.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:191
msgid ""
"In order to build pressure towards the blockade, there will be a **Countdown "
"to Rebellion starting 28th August** with local groups around the country "
"invited to cause **high impact disruption** in their own regions, to gather "
"and galvanise rebels in readiness for action and to warn the Government that "
"the **Rebellion is coming!**"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:193
msgid ""
"If we stand a chance of making this historic Rebellion successful we need to "
"grow the movement bigger than before. This Rebellion belongs to all of us, "
"so if you haven’t already, [join a local "
"group](https://rebellion.earth/act-now/local-groups/) and start using our "
"[mobilisation "
"methods](https://rebellion.earth/act-now/resources/communities/mass-mobilisation/) "
"to help grow the movement."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:195
msgid ""
"Find out more about the plans for both of these on the website "
"[here](http://rebellion.earth/uk-rebellion-2020/), [sign up "
"here](https://www.facebook.com/events/901209047010625) and invite all your "
"friends."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:197
msgid "Together we are powerful. **Crisis does not have to mean collapse.**"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:200
#, no-wrap
msgid "Indigenous Emergency"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:203
#, no-wrap
msgid "**9 AUG | Global**\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:205
msgid "![Poster for \"Indigenous Emergency.\"](/assets/uploads/13.jpg)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:207
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Indigenous people in Brazil are facing unprecedented threats:** on top of "
"attacks from government-sanctioned racism and land grabbing, the Covid-19 "
"mortality rate is much higher among Indigenous people.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:209
msgid ""
"Without much-needed medical help, many lives will be lost. **These are the "
"people on the front line of our fragile ecosystem.** Guarding the lungs of "
"the planet from big business and deforestation."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-07-16-newsletter-41.md:211
